Idempotent Producer -> Ensures no duplicate messages even if retry happens.

❌ Having more consumers than partitions wastes resources * extra consumers will remain idle

Number of consumers in a group should be ≤ number of partitions, 1 consumer can read from multiple partition

| Guarantee     | Duplicate Risk                    |
| ------------- | --------------------------------- |
| At-most-once  | No duplicate, data loss possible  |
| At-least-once | No data loss, duplicates possible |
| Exactly-once  | No loss, no duplicate             |

Offset commit strategy : enable.auto.commit=false, Use manual commit only after successful processing.

